            <h1>About Us</h1>
        </header>


        <p>
            Welcome to Free Sweet, your trusted companion on the celiac disease journey. Founded with a deep
            understanding of the challenges faced by those living gluten-free, we're a passionate team dedicated to
            making your gluten-free journey easier and more delicious. Our website offers a wealth of information,
            from understanding celiac disease to exploring a world of gluten-free recipes. Our online shop features
            a curated selection of high-quality desserts, ensuring you can enjoy sweet treats without compromise.
            Beyond recipes, we offer valuable information and support, empowering you to navigate the complexities
            of celiac disease with confidence. Join our community and connect with others who understand, sharing
            experiences and finding inspiration together.
        </p>

