    <div class="section">

        <header>
            <h1>Our Story</h1>
        </header>


        <p>
            When I was diagnosed with celiac disease, I entered a new world full of challenges. It was difficult to
            find gluten-free products, especially sweets, and when they were available, the prices were often very
            high. Over time, I realized I wasn’t the only one facing this problem.
        </p>
        <p>
            That’s why I decided to start my own project, with the goal of offering gluten-free sweets that are
            delicious in taste and affordable for everyone. I believe everyone deserves the opportunity to enjoy
            safe and healthy treats without having to pay exorbitant prices.
        </p>

        <p>
            Through this project, I aim to make the world of gluten-free sweets accessible to everyone, so that all
            can enjoy a sweet and safe experience at the same time.
        </p>

